:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"28 Best WordPress Resume Themes to Create Best Impression\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 25 Oct 2018 08:22:27 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"best responsive themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"CV themes for WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"WordPress resume\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223209\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:608:\"<p>Do you want to create an online CV and improve your online presence? With a personal resume website, you can build your brand, find jobs, make new contacts, and promote yourself professionally. Used by more than 31% of all websites online, WordPress is an ideal platform for creating your very own resume website. In this [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/\">28 Best WordPress Resume Themes to Create Best Impression</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45405:\"<p>Do you want to create an online CV and improve your online presence? With a personal resume website, you can build your brand, find jobs, make new contacts, and promote yourself professionally. Used by more than 31% of all websites online, WordPress is an ideal platform for creating your very own resume website.</p>\n<p>In this article, weâll share our handpicked list of the best WordPress resume themes with which you can easily create an online resume. Get ready to open your door, because Opportunity is about to come a-knocking!</p>\n<h3>Creating Your Resume Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>To start your WordPress resume website, youâll need a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\">domain name and a web hosting account</a>. Domain name refers to your websiteâs address on the internet, like Google.com or IsItWP.com. And, hosting refers to the physical location of your site on the internet where your siteâs content and files are stored. </p>\n<p>A domain name normally costs around $14.99 per year and a web hosting plan costs around 7.99 per month. When these costs are combined, the total cost for starting a site can be quite high for an individual such as yourself. </p>\n<p>Thankfully, you donât need to worry about the high starting cost anymore because <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> has a special discount offer for you. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/bluehost-hosting-free-business-emails.jpg\" alt=\"bluehost-hosting-free-business-emails\" width=\"745\" height=\"356\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-220096\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/bluehost-hosting-free-business-emails.jpg 745w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/bluehost-hosting-free-business-emails-300x143.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 745px) 100vw, 745px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Yes, thatâs right! Weâve made a special deal with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> to offer our users a 60% discount on hosting plus a free domain. That means youâll get hosting for just $2.75 per month and no charge at all for the domain. They&#8217;ll also provide a free SSL certificate to make your site more secure. </p>\n<p>We highly recommend you to grab this deal to get started. </p>\n<p>First, set up your hosting and domain. Then, youâll need to install WordPress&#8217; software and your resume theme. If you need detailed instructions, hereâs our step-by-step <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">guide on how to create a WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, letâs go ahead and check out 28 best WordPress resume themes for 2018. 	</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-freelo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Freelo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-freelo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/freelo-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"freelo-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"455\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223239\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/freelo-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/freelo-wordpress-theme-300x176.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/freelo-wordpress-theme-768x451.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Freelo is an elegant WordPress theme suitable for freelancers, designers, photographers, or any type of creative professionals to build an online resume or portfolio. It has powerful portfolio options like multiple portfolios, multiple portfolio animation styles, multiple portfolio view styles, shortcodes, etc. to allow you to build a complete portfolio. </p>\n<p>The theme comes with a powerful visual drag and drop page builder which makes theme customization simple and effortless. You can edit all the site elements right from the frontend with its visual editor, allowing you to see your changes instantly as you make them. </p>\n<p>Besides, you can use unlimited colors, 600+ Google fonts, unlimited sidebars, and various page and post options. Itâs a simple-yet-powerful theme that&#8217;s perfect for building a creative portfolio. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/mojomarketplace-freelo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Freelo today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shiftcv/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. ShiftCV</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shiftcv/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/shiftcv-wordpres-theme.jpg\" alt=\"shiftcv-wordpres-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"455\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223240\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/shiftcv-wordpres-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/shiftcv-wordpres-theme-300x176.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/shiftcv-wordpres-theme-768x451.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>ShiftCV is a modern WordPress theme to showcase your profile, skills, job experience, and testimonials in an eye-catching way. It also lets you provide print and download CV options on your site. </p>\n<p>It has a compact and clean design with sortable sections in a 1-page profile. However, you can also add a personal blog page to present your content in multiple formats like a blog article, audio, video, or slideshow. </p>\n<p>The theme lets you present your CV in 2 color schemes: dark or light. Itâs fully responsive which means your site will look great on all devices. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/shiftcv/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with ShiftCV today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-resume/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Resume</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-resume/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resume-tesla-themes-template.jpg\" alt=\"resume-tesla-themes-template\" width=\"704\" height=\"485\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223241\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resume-tesla-themes-template.jpg 704w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resume-tesla-themes-template-300x207.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 704px) 100vw, 704px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Resume is a stylish WordPress theme for presenting your CV in a creative way. It features a beautiful CV template with bold typography, vivid colors, smooth transitions, and effects. You can show your work skills, experience, awards, portfolio, etc. in an aesthetic way using this theme. </p>\n<p>It has a 1-page design with different bold sections like portfolio, blog, and contact. The contact section has options to show a contact form, phone number, address, and key testimonials. </p>\n<p>The theme optimized for speed to load faster, and is fully responsive so it&#8217;s adaptable to any device. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/teslathemes-resume/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Resume today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/personage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Personage</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/personage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/personage-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"personage-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"455\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223242\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/personage-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/personage-wordpress-theme-300x176.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/personage-wordpress-theme-768x451.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Personage is a professional resume WordPress theme for building an online CV. It features a sophisticated 1-page design with clean elements. To get started with your online CV quickly, you can import 1 of the 4 pre-designed demos and simply customize its content. </p>\n<p>The theme lets you present your biography, experience, education, and work in a polished way. You can also add a Print button for your resume section so people can print or download your resume in PDF or Word formats. </p>\n<p>To allow people to easily contact you, it has the option to add a contact form with a map, as well as social icons. The theme also lets you add multi-format blog posts. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/personage/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Personage today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-oneengine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. OneEngine</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-oneengine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/oneengine-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"oneengine-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"467\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223243\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/oneengine-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/oneengine-wordpress-theme-300x181.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/oneengine-wordpress-theme-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>OneEngine is a stunning 1-page WordPress theme suitable for grand online portfolios and resume websites. It features a full-width slider header with bold text and professionally-designed sections for about, skills, team, work, blog, and contact on the homepage. </p>\n<p>OneEngine has a unique style for the about section which helps you show your companyâs progress via a timeline. The portfolio section is great thanks to multiple filter options. Plus, it has a pricing table section. </p>\n<p>Itâs an easy-to-use theme that anyone can use. Try it out, play with its options, and build yourself a fantastic online portfolio or CV.  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/enginethemes-oneengine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with OneEngine today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/profession/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Profession</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/profession/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/profession-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"profession-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"467\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223244\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/profession-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/profession-wordpress-theme-300x181.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/profession-wordpress-theme-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Profession is an amazing WordPress theme to gracefully present your profession with a larger audience. It features stunning image sliders, sections for skills and achievements, a featured section for your work experience, and a contact option on the homepage. Itâs basically a 1-page theme; however, it has a beautiful blog page to present your latest articles. </p>\n<p>Profession theme is stylish as it has horizontal scrolling design as well as vertical design. Besides, it also has options to add a full-screen background or a simple background. If you want an RTL website, it has full RTL support and a pre-made RTL demo. </p>\n<p>One interesting feature of the theme is its toggle menu, which lets you show your name / site title and website menu alternatively.  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/profession/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Profession today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-nico/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Nico</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-nico/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/nico-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"nico-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"467\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223245\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/nico-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/nico-wordpress-theme-300x181.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/nico-wordpress-theme-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Nico is a simple-yet-elegant WordPress theme suitable for building an online portfolio, resume, or photography site. It comes with a truly unique design layout which helps you display your work beautifully and promote it to the next level. </p>\n<p>The theme features a filterable portfolio with cool animations that help you show your work via categories. It has flexible layout options and advanced customization options. Thereâre multiple color schemes, custom widgets, etc. </p>\n<p>It has the power of most popular page builder plugins: Elementor, Divi, and Brizy. Of these 3 plugins, you can choose 1 for customizing your site. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-nico/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Nico today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/resume-cv-vcard-portfolio/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Resume, CV, vCard &amp; Portfolio</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/resume-cv-vcard-portfolio/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resume-cv-vcardportfolio-wp-theme.jpg\" alt=\"resume-cv-vcard&amp;portfolio-wp-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"467\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223246\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resume-cv-vcardportfolio-wp-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resume-cv-vcardportfolio-wp-theme-300x181.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resume-cv-vcardportfolio-wp-theme-768x463.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Resume, CV, vCard &amp; Portfolio is the theme youâre looking for if you want to create a resume, CV, vCard, or Portfolio. The themeâs name speaks for itself actually. It features a distinct and beautiful layout to build a full-fledged resume website. </p>\n<p>The theme comes with 2 background versions: dark and light. You can import a demo with 1 click, instantly customize it, and get your website ready in no time.</p>\n<p>Thereâre unlimited color options to design different parts of the site. 