s-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ithemer-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>iThemer is a free premium WordPress theme for resume and portfolio. It comes with a featured image header with a welcome message and two buttons for hiring and your work. Moreover, it has a simple list blog layout, animated banner, about us, services, work and portfolio with fancybox, counter up, experience timeline, client and footer widgets. </p>\n<p>With iThemer, you can use Google fonts, Font Awesome icons, social links, etc. and show off your creativity. </p>\n<p>The theme allows you to import the demo content with 1 click and get started with your resume site instantly. For customizing the theme options and design, you can use the Live Customizer which lets you customize your site with real-time live previews. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ithemer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with iThemer today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Atomic</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/atomic-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"atomic-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223257\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/atomic-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/atomic-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/atomic-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Atomic is a multipurpose WordPress theme suitable for creating a portfolio as well as a business website. It comes with beautiful templates for teams, services, testimonials, portfolio, blog posts, and more. </p>\n<p>The theme has stylish typography and intuitive organization for its different site elements. It allows full customization of your site&#8217;s header by changing a header image, background color, image opacity, text, etc. </p>\n<p>Most importantly, to let you showcase your latest projects, it has options to add image galleries, videos, etc. in different styles. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/arraythemes-atomic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Atomic today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/excellent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">22. Excellent</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/excellent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/excellent-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"excellent-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223258\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/excellent-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/excellent-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/excellent-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Excellent is a freemium <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-responsive-wordpress-themes/\">responsive theme</a> for creating professional business, blog, CV, and portfolio sites. It comes with a full set of excellent features that enable you to build a great-looking resume site in no time.</p>\n<p>The theme features cool templates for portfolio, gallery, blog, testimonials, contact us, etc. You can also find custom widgets, multiple navigation and social menus, and endless color options to make your siteâs design unique. </p>\n<p>It has a handy demo for a standard CV that has a profile photo and profile details in 2 columns on the homepage. Below that, thereâs a beautiful portfolio section to showcase your latest work. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/excellent/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Excellent today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-eclipse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">23. Eclipse</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-eclipse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/eclipse-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"eclipse-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223134\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/eclipse-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/eclipse-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/eclipse-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If youâre a photographer and looking for a theme to showcase your wonderful photos, Eclipse is the perfect theme for you. The theme comes with beautiful slider options in the header, image galleries, portfolio posts, and cute blog templates. </p>\n<p>The theme provides options to add widgets in the homepage where you can add any widget you like including your about page, Instagram widget, buy option for your photo prints, etc. The theme is WooCommerce-ready so you can create a shop page and sell your photographs. </p>\n<p>Eclipse has built-in Live Customizer which allows you to change the design of your site with immediate live previews. Therefore, itâs easy and quick to customize the theme. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wpzoom-eclipse/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Eclipse today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/libretto/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">24. Libretto</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/libretto/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/libretto-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"libretto-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223259\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/libretto-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/libretto-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/libretto-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Libretto is a free responsive 1-column theme for WordPress. It features a classic style and careful typography details so that your site content looks classy. Itâs ideal for showcasing articles with large images or for photo stories with inspirational quotes. So, if youâre an inspirational photographer, itâs a perfect theme to start your resume website. </p>\n<p>Libretto provides beautiful templates for blog, about, and contact page.  The theme is so simple and easy to use that even a person with absolutely no coding skills can build a complete site using this theme. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/libretto/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Libretto today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">25. Resumee</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resumee-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"resumee-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"475\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223260\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resumee-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resumee-wordpress-theme-300x184.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/resumee-wordpress-theme-768x471.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Resumee is simple WordPress resume theme for professionals. It has a clean design with an all white background. You can add a profile photo, social links, contact details, and a short bio at the top of your homepage. </p>\n<p>Itâs basically a 1-page theme with different sections for work experience, education, and skills right on the homepage. Itâs a direct and distraction-free minimalist resume theme. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/resumee/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Resume today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/idyllic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">26. Idyllic</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/idyllic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/idyllic-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"idyllic-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"475\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223261\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/idyllic-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/idyllic-wordpress-theme-300x184.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/idyllic-wordpress-theme-768x471.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Idyllic is a beautiful multipurpose theme for WordPress that you can use for creating a variety of websites. With its extended features and options, you can use it for business, portfolio, blog, or online resume website. </p>\n<p>The theme comes with multiple sections as well as widgets on the front page. Thereâre multiple navigation and social menus, logo upload, and color options. For showcasing your selected works and latest projects, it has several fabulous portfolio layouts. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/idyllic/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Idyllic today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/orfeo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">27. Orfeo</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/orfeo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/orfeo-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"orfeo-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"443\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223262\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/orfeo-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/orfeo-wordpress-theme-300x171.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/orfeo-wordpress-theme-768x439.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Orfeo is a responsive 1-page WordPress theme designed for multipurpose sites. You can build corporate business sites as well as a blog, portfolio, or online resume site using this theme. It features beautifully-designed sections for features, team, testimonials, products, pricing, blog, contact, etc. </p>\n<p>If youâre an entrepreneur, blogger, or a student, this theme provides you with ample features to create your impressive online portfolio. You can use custom backgrounds, mega menus, etc. and customize the entire theme&#8217;s options from its Live Customizer. </p>\n<p>Itâs an SEO optimized and fast loading theme that lets you create a truly powerful site. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/orfeo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Orfeo today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/mcluhan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">28. McLuhan</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/mcluhan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mcluhan-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"mcluhan-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"455\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223263\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mcluhan-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mcluhan-wordpress-theme-300x176.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mcluhan-wordpress-theme-768x451.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>McLuhan is a free WordPress theme with a simple and clean design. It features a front page with a complete post archive arranged by year to give your users a quick glimpse of your work via the custom timeline. </p>\n<p>With McLuhan, you can get 2 predefined page templates: a resume page template and a full-width template. Using the resume template, you can easily create your online resume. </p>\n<p>The theme allows you to customize background colors for the sidebar and content, plus add social links and icons. It has an AJAX-powered mobile search with instant results. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/mcluhan/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with McLuhan today!</a></p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you to find the best WordPress resume themes for creating an online resume, CV, and portfolio. You may also want to see our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/legit-ways-to-make-money-online-blogging/\">how to make money from online blogging</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/\">28 Best WordPress Resume Themes to Create Best Impression</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-resume-themes/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:54:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"WPForms vs. Gravity Forms â Best Form Plugin Showdown\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wpforms-vs-gravity-forms/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wpforms-vs-gravity-forms/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 24 Oct 2018 10:54:19 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:5:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"WordPress Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:43:\"comparison between wpforms vs gravity forms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"gravity forms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"wpforms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"wpforms vs gravity forms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222320\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:620:\"<p>WPForms vs. Gravity Forms: who would win? If youâre asking that, then youâre probably looking for the best plugin to create a WordPress contact form for your users to get in touch with you. WordPress offers many contact form plugins with different functionalities, but WPForms and Gravity Forms are the most popular plugins of them [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wpforms-vs-gravity-forms/\">WPForms vs. Gravity Forms &#8211; Best Form Plugin Showdown</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18706:\"<p>WPForms vs. Gravity Forms: who would win? If youâre asking that, then youâre probably looking for the best plugin to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/add-contact-form-wordpress-website/\">create a WordPress contact form</a> for your users to get in touch with you.</p>\n<p>WordPress offers many contact form plugins with different functionalities, but <a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms</a> and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gravity-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gravity Forms</a> are the most popular plugins of them all. But which&#8217;s the best?</p>\n<p>In this article, weâll compare WPForms vs. Gravity Forms, in-depth, so you can make your final decision.</p>\n<h3>General Overview: WPForms vs. Gravity Forms</h3>\n<p>Before we start with the features, pricing, and other areas of interest, let&#8217;s give you a basic introduction of both <a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms</a> and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gravity-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gravity Forms</a> plugins.</p>\n<h3>What&#8217;s WPForms?</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg\" alt=\"WPForms\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222076\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/wpforms-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms</a> is the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)\">best contact form plugin</a> for WordPress websites. It offers the most beginner-friendly form builder, which can help with easily creating WordPress forms.</p>\n<p>Everything is drag and drop with WPForms, so you can quickly set up your contact form with the fields you need. It has multiple built-in templates in the form builder which can be used to launch WordPress forms in 1 click. You can easily customize pre-built form templates using the drag and drop functionality.</p>\n<p>It reduces the time spent on creating forms from hours to mere minutes. Whether you want to create a contact form or a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/custom-user-registration-form-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create a Custom User Registration Form in WordPress\">user registration form</a>, it&#8217;s quite simple using WPForms templates.</p>\n<p>Additionally, WPForms has multiple premium addons that give you instant access to amazing features like adding polls and survey forms in WordPress. WPForms commits to excellence with the needs of their users constantly in mind.</p>\n<h3>What&#8217;s Gravity Forms?</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/gravityforms-wp-plugin.jpg\" alt=\"gravityforms-wp-plugin\" width=\"775\" height=\"333\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221324\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/gravityforms-wp-plugin.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/gravityforms-wp-plugin-300x129.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/gravityforms-wp-plugin-768x330.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gravity-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gravity Forms</a> is one of the most popular form builder plugins for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress websites</a>. It can be used to create all types of forms in WordPress. It comes with a form builder that helps you create simple-to-complex forms with ease.</p>\n<p>When we talk about features, Gravity Forms stands out as being the most powerful plugin, with super-flexible functionalities. You can easily create responsive forms with spam filters, add payment gateways, launch surveys, get online bookings, and more.</p>\n<p>Gravity Forms has everything you need to create WordPress forms. It&#8217;s a premium plugin with exceptional addons to add forms on your website.</p>\n<h3>Ease of Use</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms</a> offers a simple drag and drop form builder that can be used to easily create WordPress forms in few minutes. You don&#8217;t need to hire a developer or write any code to create your forms.</p>\n<p>It allows you to easily add or remove form fields. You can also rearrange fields in your WordPress forms with the WPForms drag and drop functionality. It shows a live preview of the changes you&#8217;ve made, so you don&#8217;t need to shift your browser tabs to see your form in action.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-review-1.png\" alt=\"wpforms review\" width=\"775\" height=\"468\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-219789\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-review-1.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-review-1-300x181.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-review-1-768x464.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>It comes with multiple built-in form templates that are designed to fulfill the needs of all varieties of WordPress websites. These templates include a blank canvas, simple contact form, request a quote, donation, newsletter sign up, and other useful forms that can be launched in 1 click.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms</a> offers several addons to add more features to your WordPress forms plugin. These addons include additional form templates, payment gateways, email marketing services, and more.</p>\n<p>You can easily embed a form in your WordPress pages, posts, and widget-ready areas using WPForms. It comes with a WPForms widget that allows you to display any of your forms in the sidebar, footer, or other widget areas of your website.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-embed-form.gif\" alt=\"wpforms embed form\" width=\"614\" height=\"470\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-219787\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gravity-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gravity Forms</a> has an intuitive drag and drop form builder that allows you to easily add form fields and quickly create a WordPress form. It also allows you to create complex forms easily. However, there&#8217;s a bit of learning curve when using Gravity Forms.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/formbuilder.png\" alt=\"Gravity Forms - Drag and drop form builder\" width=\"712\" height=\"310\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-477\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/formbuilder.png 712w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/formbuilder-300x131.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 712px) 100vw, 712px\" /></p>\n<p>You start by adding a name for your form and then click to next screen to add form fields. There&#8217;s no preview of the form fields on the same page, so you&#8217;ll need to click on the &#8216;Preview&#8217; button every time in the form builder to view your changes.</p>\n<p>With Gravity Forms, you&#8217;ll need to manually add the form fields every time as there&#8217;re no form templates available.</p>\n<p><strong>Winner</strong>: WPForms</p>\n<h3>Price</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms</a> has multiple pricing plans from budget to business websites. Their basic plan starts from $49 / year which is suitable for most personal websites and blogs.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-pricing.png\" alt=\"wpforms pricing\" width=\"775\" height=\"481\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-219788\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-pricing.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-pricing-300x186.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/wpforms-pricing-768x477.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>They have plans for small businesses, non-profit organizations, eCommerce stores, or any other variety of website. WPForms offers best prices for all sizes and budgets.</p>\n<p>If you want to test the WPForms plugin before purchasing it, then simply download the lite version, easily available in the WordPress plugins repository. You can upgrade to a premium plan later and enjoy the super-flexible features within your budget.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gravity-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gravity Forms</a> offers basic to elite licenses for WordPress users. Their pricing starts from $59 / year for single site license which is a bit expensive in comparison to WPForms. You&#8217;ll need to upgrade to their Pro plan to add features which is even more expensive.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/gravity-forms-pricing.png\" alt=\"gravity forms pricing\" width=\"740\" height=\"369\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222265\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/gravity-forms-pricing.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/gravity-forms-pricing-300x150.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>All the licenses allow you to create unlimited forms. You&#8217;ll also get 1 year of support and updates. Their Elite license is the most expensive and most complete WordPress forms solution. It includes priority support, all Gravity Forms addons, and lifetime updates.</p>\n<p><strong>Winner</strong>: WPForms</p>\n<h3>Features</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms</a> is a feature-rich contact form plugin. It allows you to create simple-to-advanced forms easily. Let&#8217;s take a look at few of the most notable features that make WPFomrs the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Contact Form Plugins Compared (2018)\">best contact form plugin</a> available.</p>\n<p><strong>1. Poll / Survey Form</strong></p>\n<p>The Poll / Survey Form addon by WPForms allows you to easily add online polls and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-a-survey-in-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Survey in WordPress (Step by Step)\">surveys in WordPress</a>. It supports all the features you&#8217;ll need for your poll / survey form.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/survey-poll-voting-min.gif\" alt=\"wpforms survey poll voting\" width=\"562\" height=\"455\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-219784\" /></p>\n<p>The poll / survey addon can combine with WPForms&#8217; conditional logic to personalize the survey questions on users&#8217; answers. You can easily get user feedback and display interactive survey reports on your website.</p>\n<p><strong>2. User Registration Form</strong></p>\n<p>The User Registration addon by WPForms allows you to quickly create user login / <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/custom-user-registration-form-wordpress/\" title=\"How to Create a Custom User Registration Form in WordPress\">registration forms in WordPress</a>. It gives your users instant access to login or sign up from anywhere on your website. Your users won&#8217;t need to visit the default WordPress login page every time they want to sign in.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/userregform.jpg\" alt=\"User registration form\" width=\"775\" height=\"423\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-221584\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/userregform.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/userregform-300x164.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/userregform-768x419.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>You can embed the user registration form in your WordPress pages, posts, or widget-ready areas. The user registration form is useful for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-membership-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Membership Plugins Compared (2018)\">memberships sites</a>, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-ecommerce-plugins-compared/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress eCommerce Plugins Compared (2018)\">eCommerce stores</a>, forums, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Post Submission Form</strong></p>\n<p>If you want to allow your users to write guest posts for your website, then you can create an interactive post submission form using the Post Submission addon by WPForms. You can also set up the post submission form to collect users&#8217; feedback, testimonials, reviews, and other user-generated content.</p>\n<p>This addon is super-flexible at automatically adding newly-submitted guest posts into the WordPress post editor for you to review and publish on your website.</p>\n<p><strong>4. Payment Solutions</strong></p>\n<p>WPForms integrates with PayPal Standard and Stripe for your online payments. It&#8217;s best for collecting donations, selling products online, and any other situation that needs an online payment solution.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/payments-tab-wpforms.png\" alt=\"payments tab wpforms\" width=\"775\" height=\"498\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-219795\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/payments-tab-wpforms.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/payments-tab-wpforms-300x193.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/payments-tab-wpforms-768x494.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>WPForms shows your product photos in the order form, so your users can pay freely and see what they are purchasing.</p>\n<p>WPForms has many other useful addons including email marketing services, captcha, geolocation, signature, offline forms, and more. These addons make WPForms a powerful WordPress form plugin.</p>\n<h3>Features: Gravity Forms</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gravity-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gravity Forms</a> is a fantastic WordPress form plugin to create complex forms with ease. They offer several useful features that can take your WordPress forms experience to the next level, and the list is ever-growing. Let&#8217;s take a look at the most important features of Gravity Forms.</p>\n<p><strong>1. 30+ form fields</strong></p>\n<p>Gravity Forms has over 30 form fields that can be used to create any kind of form you desire in WordPress. You can use the drag and drop functionality to easily add the fields onto your WordPress form.</p>\n<p><strong>2. Conditional Logic</strong></p>\n<p>It&#8217;s the smartest feature and allows you to add users&#8217; based fields in your WordPress forms. You can easily show or hide fields based on users&#8217; selections. It&#8217;s also helpful when you want to create a smart survey form and change questions on the basis of answers from your users.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Spam Filter</strong></p>\n<p>Gravity Forms integrates easily with all the useful spam filtration plugins like Google reCaptcha, Really Simple Captcha, and Akismet to block spam form submissions in WordPress.</p>\n<p><strong>4. File Uploads</strong></p>\n<p>It&#8217;s one of the most useful features when you want your users to upload files in your form. Many Human Resource companies add this feature on their websites to collect resumes from their visitors. You can use it in your WordPress form to easily get files from your users.</p>\n<p><strong>5. Calculations</strong></p>\n<p>You can perform advanced calculations on the basis of field values submitted by your users. It can be useful for forex websites and other money exchange businesses. </p>\n<p><strong>6. Front-End Forms</strong></p>\n<p>Gravity Forms allows you to add front-end forms on your WordPress website to easily gather blog post submissions. You can allow users to submit their articles without having access to your WordPress dashboard.</p>\n<p><strong>7. Integration with Apps</strong></p>\n<p>Gravity Forms integrates with nearly all online apps including email marketing services, payments, CRMs, etc. It works great with all the popular payment solutions out of the box.</p>\n<p>Gravity Forms has many other impressive features for your WordPress forms. It also works great with all the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\" title=\"27 Best WordPress Plugins that You MUST Use (2018)\">best WordPress plugins</a> to add more features and flexibility to your forms.</p>\n<p><strong>Winner</strong>: Gravity Forms</p>\n<h3>Documentation and Support</h3>\n<p>WPForms is well-known for their documentation and support. Their features and addons are well-explained in the extensive documentation, covering every factor you&#8217;d need to know to create your forms in WordPress. You can also refer to their blog for more-detailed articles on each feature.</p>\n<p>Support is offered by a ticket-based email support system. Their support is fast and highly rated in their user reviews.</p>\n<p>On the other hand, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gravity-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gravity Forms</a> has extensive documentation that guides you through easily creating WordPress forms. Their support is distributed according to the license you purchase. The Elite license has priority support, while other licenses have 1 year of ticket-based support.</p>\n<p><strong>Winner</strong>: Tie</p>\n<h3>Conclusion</h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://wpforms.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WPForms</a> is the best choice for everyone regardless of their budget. It includes all the necessary features and flexibility you need to create a WordPress form.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/gravity-forms/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gravity Forms</a> is best for users who want to build advanced or very complex forms. It has a variety of features with no match. However, it&#8217;s a bit more expensive than WPForms, especially when comparing the basic &#8220;starter&#8221; offerings.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you choose between WPForms vs. Gravity Forms. If you liked this post, you might also enjoy our in-depth <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wpforms/\" title=\"WPForms Review 2018: Is It the Best WordPress Contact Form Plugin?\">review of the WPForms plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wpforms-vs-gravity-forms/\">WPForms vs. Gravity Forms &#8211; Best Form Plugin Showdown</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:53:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wpforms-vs-gravity-forms/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"How to Create a WordPress Site-Specific Plugin (Easy Guide)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 23 Oct 2018 08:05:50 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"code snippet\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"functions.php\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"site specific plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223680\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:657:\"<p>Want to create a site-specific WordPress plugin on your site? Creating a site-specific plugin is one of the best ways to add custom functions to your WordPress site. In this article, weâll explain everything you need to know about using a site-specific WordPress plugin. Extending Your Website Features with a Site-Specific Plugin WordPress is so [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/\">How to Create a WordPress Site-Specific Plugin (Easy Guide)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9423:\"<p>Want to create a site-specific WordPress plugin on your site? Creating a site-specific plugin is one of the best ways to add custom functions to your WordPress site. In this article, weâll explain everything you need to know about using a site-specific WordPress plugin.</p>\n<h3>Extending Your Website Features with a Site-Specific Plugin</h3>\n<p>WordPress is so flexible that it allows you to easily enhance the functionalities of your site on your own without hiring a developer. You can enhance the functionalities in two ways â either by installing a plugin or adding a custom code snippet to your site.</p>\n<p>Although installing a plugin is an obvious way (especially for non-developers) to extend your siteâs functionality, at times, itâs hard to find a plugin that exactly addresses your needs. On the flip side, you can find WordPress tutorials that recommend adding a code snippet to solve your exact needs.</p>\n<p>There are two ways to add a code snippet to your WordPress website in order to enhance the functionalities:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Build a site-specific plugin and add a custom code snippet to it.</li>\n<li>Insert a snippet to your functions.php file.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>The main drawback of copying a snippet to your functions.php file is that the functionality will disappear when you switch over to a new <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\">WordPress theme</a>. This is where a site-specific plugin comes in.</p>\n<p>A site-specific WordPress plugin is independent of your theme, which allows you to add custom snippets to your site.</p>\n<p>Letâs take a look at how to use a site-specific WordPress plugin on your site.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Method 1: Using the Code Snippets plugin (the easy way)</li>\n<li>Method 2: Using a site-specific plugin (manual creation)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Method #1: Using the Code Snippets Plugin (the Easy Way)</h3>\n<p>If you&#8217;re not interested in creating a site-specific plugin manually, which can be time-consuming, then this method is for you.</p>\n<p>Go ahead and simply install and activate the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/code-snippets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Code Snippets</a> plugin on your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">WordPress site</a>. This plugin provides a graphical interface for managing snippets similar to the Plugins menu. You can activate or deactivate Snippets, just like plugins. Once the plugin is activated, you can find a WordPress admin menu, Snippets.</p>\n<p>To add a custom code snippet, go to <strong>Snippets &raquo; Add New</strong> and then copy the snippet to the <strong>Code</strong> field. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/custom-snippets-plugin.png\" alt=\"custom snippets plugin\" width=\"720\" height=\"488\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223672\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/custom-snippets-plugin.png 720w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/custom-snippets-plugin-300x203.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\" /></p>\n<p>Make sure to specify a title, description, and tags for your snippet as reference for yourself down the line. Once done, click <strong>Save Changes and Activate</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2.png\" alt=\"add custom snippet with custom snippets plugin\" width=\"727\" height=\"415\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223697\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2.png 727w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-custom-snippet-with-custom-snippets-plugin2-300x171.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 727px) 100vw, 727px\" /></p>\n<p>To manage your snippets, you can click onÂ <strong>All Snippets</strong> menu. Here, you can activate or deactivate the snippets, just like <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-plugins/\">WordPress plugins</a>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/manage-your-snippets.png\" alt=\"manage your snippets\" width=\"740\" height=\"409\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223673\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/manage-your-snippets.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/manage-your-snippets-300x166.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<h3>Method #2: Using a Site-Specific Plugin (Manual Creation)</h3>\n<p><strong>Step 1: Create a Site-Specific Plugin</strong></p>\n<p>Open a text editor on your computer, such as Notepad or TextEdit. Your plugin file needs a specific header code so that WordPress can recognize it as a plugin. Let&#8217;s copy the following header code to your Notepad.</p>\n<pre class=\"brush: php; title: ; notranslate\">\n&lt;?php\n/*\nPlugin Name: Site Plugin for example.com\nDescription: Site specific code changes for example.com\n*/\n/* Start Adding Functions Below this Line */\n  \n  \n/* Stop Adding Functions Below this Line */\n?&gt;\n</pre>\n<p>Letâs name our site-specific plugin file as <strong>custom-snippets.php</strong>. Bear in mind that in order to save your file as a PHP file, you&#8217;ll need to choose <strong>All Files</strong> as your <strong>Save as type</strong>. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/save-your-site-specific-plugin.png\" alt=\"save your site-specific plugin\" width=\"691\" height=\"492\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223674\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/save-your-site-specific-plugin.png 691w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/save-your-site-specific-plugin-300x214.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 691px) 100vw, 691px\" /></p>\n<p>Now create a new folder named <strong>custom-snippets</strong> and move the PHP file youâve just created to the folder.</p>\n<p>Next, youâll need to compress your site-specific plugin folder, custom-snippets. Hereâs how to do it.</p>\n<p>Windows users can right-click on the folder and then click <strong>Send to &raquo; Compressed (zipped) folder</strong>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/create-a-site-specific-plugin.png\" alt=\"create a site-specific plugin\" width=\"680\" height=\"462\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223678\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/create-a-site-specific-plugin.png 680w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/create-a-site-specific-plugin-300x204.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px\" /></p>\n<p>If youâre on Mac, right click and select <strong>Compress âcustom-snippetsâ</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 2: Install the Site-Specific Plugin </strong></p>\n<p>Now that you have created the pluginâs zip file, go to your WordPress dashboard and upload it by navigating to <strong>Plugins &raquo; Add New</strong>. Then click <strong>Upload Plugin</strong>. Youâll now be prompted to choose the right plugin file and install it.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/upload-a-plugin.png\" alt=\"upload a WordPress plugin\" width=\"741\" height=\"434\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223675\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/upload-a-plugin.png 741w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/upload-a-plugin-300x176.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 741px) 100vw, 741px\" /></p>\n<p>After installing the plugin, go ahead and activate it so you can start using the site-specific plugin.</p>\n<p><strong>Step 3: Using the Site-Specific Plugin</strong></p>\n<p>In order to add a snippet to your recently uploaded site-specific plugin, go to <strong>Plugins &raquo; Editor</strong>. On the right-hand side, you can see a dropdown menu <strong>Select plugin to edit</strong>. Letâs choose <strong>Custom Snippet </strong>and then click <strong>Select</strong>. Youâll now be directed to the <strong>custom-snippets.php</strong> file of your plugin.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin.png\" alt=\"add your snippets to site-specific plugin\" width=\"748\" height=\"378\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223677\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin.png 748w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/add-your-snippets-to-site-specific-plugin-300x152.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 748px) 100vw, 748px\" /></p>\n<p>Here, you can add the snippet of your choice below the line: /* Start Adding Functions Below this Line */</p>\n<p>After inserting your snippet, click on <strong>Update File</strong>.</p>\n<p>Thatâs it!</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you learn how to create and use a site-specific plugin on your WordPress site. Now go ahead and <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/snippets/\">find some code snippets</a> that you can add to enhance your WordPress functionalities.</p>\n<p>You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/fix-error-establishing-database-connection-wordpress-step-step/\">fixing the error establishing database connection in WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/\">How to Create a WordPress Site-Specific Plugin (Easy Guide)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.isitwp.com/create-wordpress-site-specific-plugin-easy-guide/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"How to Set Up Google Analytics eCommerce Tracking for WooCommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://www.isitwp.com/google-analytics-ecommerce-tracking-woocommerce/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://www.isitwp.com/google-analytics-ecommerce-tracking-woocommerce/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 22 Oct 2018 08:24:28 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:6:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:19:\"WordPress Tutorials\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"ecommerce tracking for woocommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"google analytics ecommerce tracking\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"google analytics ecommerce tracking for woocommerce\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"how to set up google analytics ecommerce tracking\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:42:\"set up google analytics ecommerce tracking\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=222630\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:650:\"<p>Do you want to set up Google Analytics eCommerce tracking for your online store? Tracking your WooCommerce store will help you improve the user&#8217;s journey and increase your sales. It&#8217;s a common practice to learn which products are selling the most in your online store. In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to easily set [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/google-analytics-ecommerce-tracking-woocommerce/\">How to Set Up Google Analytics eCommerce Tracking for WooCommerce</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11472:\"<p>Do you want to set up Google Analytics eCommerce tracking for your online store? Tracking your WooCommerce store will help you improve the user&#8217;s journey and increase your sales. It&#8217;s a common practice to learn which products are selling the most in your online store.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll show you how to easily set up Google Analytics eCommerce tracking for your WooCommerce store.</p>\n<h3>What is eCommerce Tracking and How&#8217;s It Different?</h3>\n<p>You probably already monitor the traffic of your website / blog with Google Analytics. It allows you to optimize your site for the users, so you can get more traffic. You might also monitor the traffic of your WooCommerce store as a general website on Google Analytics.</p>\n<p>Likewise, eCommerce tracking (more precisely-enhanced eCommerce tracking) is also an option in the Google Analytics dashboard gives you complete insights into the purchases on your store. It&#8217;ll help you understand your potential clients, so you can improve the most visited product pages and make them even better for your customers.</p>\n<p>However, you&#8217;ll need to enable the enhanced Google Analytics eCommerce tracking for <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a> to track the shopping behavior of your clients. Enhanced eCommerce tracking will help you extract a few important reports in Google Analytics like shopping behavior, checkout behavior, product lists performance, sales performance, marketing reports, and more.</p>\n<p>These reports add huge benefits to your WooCommerce store. Let&#8217;s discuss some of the reports in detail.</p>\n<h3>Shopping Behavior Report</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shopping-behavior-analysis.png\" alt=\"shopping behavior analysis\" width=\"740\" height=\"359\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223509\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shopping-behavior-analysis.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shopping-behavior-analysis-300x146.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/shopping-behavior-analysis-330x160.png 330w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>It&#8217;s a powerful report that gives you a thorough overview of your customer&#8217;s journey. You can track each client to find out the product views, hits on the checkout button, finished purchases, and payment processes.</p>\n<p>Furthermore, it&#8217;ll give you insight into where your customer&#8217;s journey breaks. For example, if a client hit the checkout button but never completed the purchase. You can then improve the specific process on your WooCommerce store so your customers finish their purchases and make payments.</p>\n<h3>Product Lists Performance Report</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/product-list-performance-report.png\" alt=\"product list performance report\" width=\"726\" height=\"442\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223513\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/product-list-performance-report.png 726w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/product-list-performance-report-300x183.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 726px) 100vw, 726px\" /></p>\n<p>It&#8217;s an important report to map a customer&#8217;s journey on your product pages. With product lists, you can set up upselling and cross selling for your customers. This report shows you the performance of the related product lists. Since it&#8217;s a revenue generator for your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-create-an-online-store-step-by-step/\">online store</a>, you should make sure the product lists are managed properly.</p>\n<p>You can also monitor an individual product&#8217;s performance and identify the complete details about upsells, number of orders, cancellations, and more.</p>\n<h3>Marketing Reports</h3>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/product-coupon.png\" alt=\"product coupon\" width=\"740\" height=\"314\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223510\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/product-coupon.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/product-coupon-300x127.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>Many online stores create marketing strategies and want to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-google-analytics-wordpress-site/\">set up Google Analytics tracking</a> for each campaign separately. The marketing reports in Google Analytics&#8217; eCommerce tracking for your WooCommerce store does just that.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re working with affiliates, then you can easily track the stats on which affiliate is sending the most customers to your store. In the detailed insights, you can monitor revenue, number of orders, successful transactions, and more.</p>\n<p>You can also set up tracking for your coupon codes. It allows you to get complete data on which coupon code has the most sales and vice versa.</p>\n<h3>Setting Up Google Analytics eCommerce Tracking for WooCommerce</h3>\n<p>The first thing you&#8217;ll need to do is install and activate the <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"MonsterInsights\">MonsterInsights</a> plugin. For more details, see our step-by-step guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/install-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"How to Install a WordPress Plugin\">how to install a WordPress plugin</a>.</p>\n<p>Upon activation, you&#8217;ll need to visit the <strong>Insights &raquo; Settings</strong> page. From there, click on the <strong>Authenticate with your Google account</strong> button.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/authenticatega.jpg\" alt=\"Authenticate with your Google account\" width=\"775\" height=\"185\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222635\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/authenticatega.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/authenticatega-300x72.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/authenticatega-768x183.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>For complete instructions, you should follow this guide on <a href=\"https://www.monsterinsights.com/docs/connect-google-analytics/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"How to Connect to Google Analytics\">how to properly connect Google Analytics with MonsterInsights</a>.</p>\n<p>After successful connection, you&#8217;ll need to visit <strong>Insights &raquo; Addons</strong> to install and activate the MonsterInsights eCommerce addon.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ecommerceaddon.jpg\" alt=\"eCommerce addon\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222636\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ecommerceaddon.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ecommerceaddon-300x155.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ecommerceaddon-768x396.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></p>\n<p>Once activated, log in to your <a href=\"https://analytics.google.com/analytics/web/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Google Analytics\" rel=\"nofollow\">Google Analytics</a> dashboard. Next, you&#8217;ll need to click on your website name where you want to set up eCommerce tracking.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/googleanalyticsproperty.jpg\" alt=\"Your website in Google Analytics account\" width=\"420\" height=\"239\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222286\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/googleanalyticsproperty.jpg 420w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/googleanalyticsproperty-300x171.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 420px) 100vw, 420px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, go to the <strong>Admin</strong> settings in the left-hand sidebar.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/admin.jpg\" alt=\"Admin\" width=\"255\" height=\"281\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222638\" /></p>\n<p>On this page, you&#8217;ll need to go to <strong>eCommerce Settings</strong> on the right side of your screen.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ecommerce-settings.jpg\" alt=\"Ecommerce settings\" width=\"540\" height=\"316\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222639\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ecommerce-settings.jpg 540w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ecommerce-settings-300x176.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" /></p>\n<p>Next, enable the <strong>Status</strong> and <strong>Related Products</strong> options. We&#8217;ve discussed these options above in the introduction.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/enable-related-products.jpg\" alt=\"Enable ecommerce settings\" width=\"453\" height=\"326\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222640\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/enable-related-products.jpg 453w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/enable-related-products-300x216.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 453px) 100vw, 453px\" /></p>\n<p>Once enabled, click on the <strong>Next</strong> button to continue.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;ll display the <strong>Enhanced eCommerce Settings</strong> option. You need to enable this reporting option to view all the reports in Google Analytics.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/enable-enhanced-ecommerce-1.jpg\" alt=\"Enable enhanced ecommerce settings\" width=\"379\" height=\"215\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222641\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/enable-enhanced-ecommerce-1.jpg 379w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/enable-enhanced-ecommerce-1-300x170.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 379px) 100vw, 379px\" /></p>\n<p>Now, go back to your WordPress Admin area. Visit the <strong>Insights &raquo; Settings</strong> page and click on the <strong>Tracking</strong> tab. In the left-hand menu, go to <strong>eCommerce</strong> and click the <strong>Use Enhanced eCommerce</strong> setting.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/use-enhanced-ecommerce.jpg\" alt=\"Use enhanced ecommerce option\" width=\"540\" height=\"411\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-222643\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/use-enhanced-ecommerce.jpg 540w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/use-enhanced-ecommerce-300x228.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" /></p>\n<p>That&#8217;s all. You can now view the complete reports for your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a> store with MonsterInsights&#8217; Google Analytics eCommerce tracking.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you learn how to set up Google Analytics eCommerce tracking for WooCommerce. You may also want to check out our guide on <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/set-download-tracking-wordpress-google-analytics/\" title=\"How to Set Up Download Tracking in WordPress With Google Analytics\">how to set up download tracking in WordPress with Google Analytics</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/google-analytics-ecommerce-tracking-woocommerce/\">How to Set Up Google Analytics eCommerce Tracking for WooCommerce</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://www.isitwp.com/google-analytics-ecommerce-tracking-woocommerce/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"Formidable Forms Review: Build Advanced WordPress Forms\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:58:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/formidable-forms/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/formidable-forms/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 19 Oct 2018 21:38:10 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?post_type=isitwp_plugin&p=223635\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:651:\"<p>Are you considering purchasing Formidable Forms but wondering if itâs the best choice? We understand. Formidable Forms is an advanced form builder plugin for WordPress, but it&#8217;s impossible to tell if it&#8217;s suitable for your needs without an in-depth analysis. In our Formidable Forms review, weâll take a look at its features, pricing, and more. [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/formidable-forms/\">Formidable Forms Review: Build Advanced WordPress Forms</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Shahzad Saeed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8253:\"<p>Are you considering purchasing Formidable Forms but wondering if itâs the best choice? We understand. Formidable Forms is an advanced form builder plugin for WordPress, but it&#8217;s impossible to tell if it&#8217;s suitable for your needs without an in-depth analysis. In our Formidable Forms review, weâll take a look at its features, pricing, and more.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-review.png\" alt=\"formidable forms review\" width=\"775\" height=\"350\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223636\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-review.png 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-review-300x135.png 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-review-768x347.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>About Formidable Forms (Formerly Formidable Pro)</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Formidable Forms</a> is a WordPress form builder that lets you easily build advanced forms without having to hire a developer. From simple contact form to complex multi-page forms, you can build any type of web form you can imagine with Formidable Forms.</p>\n<p>The lite version of the plugin is available to download for free from the WordPress.org repository. However, the lite version only lets you build a basic contact form. For advanced forms, youâll need to upgrade to the pro version.</p>\n<h3>Formidable Forms Review: Creating a Basic Form</h3>\n<p>Like most modern form builder plugins for WordPress, Formidable comes with a drag and drop builder. Letâs take a look at <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/add-contact-form-wordpress-website/\">how to build a basic contact form</a> with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Formidable Forms</a> to see how it works.</p>\n<p>The interface of <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Formidable Forms</a> is somewhat similar to Gravity Forms.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-builder.png\" alt=\"formidable forms builder\" width=\"740\" height=\"443\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223638\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-builder.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-forms-builder-300x180.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>All the fields are neatly organized in the right-hand panel. To educate you on how to use the plugin as you go, they&#8217;ve put clear instructions with arrows within the builder.</p>\n<p>To add a form field to your builder, simply click on any field in the right-hand panel. To change the layout, you can click on the Layout tab. Youâll then be prompted to choose from a variety of different form layouts.</p>\n<p>Upon creating a form, youâll be directed to the General Settings page. Here, you can choose a custom thank you message, custom styling styling options, button options, and more.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/general-settings-form-builder.png\" alt=\"general settings form builder\" width=\"528\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223640\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/general-settings-form-builder.png 528w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/general-settings-form-builder-300x257.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 528px) 100vw, 528px\" /></p>\n<h3>Building Advanced Forms with Formidable Forms</h3>\n<p>Whether you want to build a basic form or create a complex online application, <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Formidable Forms</a> helps you do it without touching a single line of code. The interface is immensely user-friendly for both beginners and advanced users alike. Letâs take a look at some advanced features in Formidable Pro.</p>\n<p><strong>1. Choose a Different Layout</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/css-layout_sidebar.gif\" alt=\"css layout sidebar\" width=\"741\" height=\"213\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223637\" /></p>\n<p>Formidable Forms is shipped with multiple layout options that look great and fit perfectly with your <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/top-wordpress-themes/\">WordPress theme</a>. You can find the Layout tab next to the Fields tab in the right-hand panel.</p>\n<p><strong>2. Advanced Fields</strong></p>\n<p>Out of the box, Formidable Pro comes with a ton of advanced form fields, such as File Upload, Rich Text, Password, Credit Card, etc.</p>\n<p><strong>3. Advanced Features </strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/create-view_calendar.gif\" alt=\"date on frontend\" width=\"631\" height=\"276\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223641\" /></p>\n<p>Formidable Pro is shipped with a wide variety of unique advanced features, such as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Display data on frontend</strong>: Formidable Forms is the only <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-contact-form-plugins/\">form builder plugin</a> that lets you display form data on the frontend.</li>\n<li><strong>Multi-page form</strong>: Reduce form abandonment by building a multi-page form with a progress bar.</li>\n<li><strong>Graph and chart</strong>: Communicate complex data trends with graphs and charts.</li>\n<li><strong>Calculation</strong>: Perform advanced numeric calculations &#8211; especially handy for eCommerce stores.</li>\n<li>And moreâ¦</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Formidable Forms: Pricing and Support</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Formidable Forms</a> offers a free version, which is available to download from the WordPress.org repository. The free version lets you build a basic contact form on your site.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-pro-review-pricing.png\" alt=\"formidable pro review- pricing\" width=\"740\" height=\"315\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223639\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-pro-review-pricing.png 740w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/formidable-pro-review-pricing-300x128.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 740px) 100vw, 740px\" /></p>\n<p>If you want to build complex forms or online applications with Formidable Forms, youâll need to purchase the pro version. The pro version is available in 4 different plans:</p>\n<p><strong>Personal</strong>: For $49, youâll get the premium 1-year license with 1 year of standard support.</p>\n<p><strong>Creator</strong>: For $99, you can use the plugin on up to 3 sites. Youâll also get addons, including MailChimp integration, MailPoet integration, Bootstrap addons, and user tracking and locations addons.</p>\n<p><strong>Business</strong>: For $199, youâll get priority support and powerful addons such as PayPal Standard, Zapier, user registration, AWeber, and more.</p>\n<p><strong>Enterprise</strong>: For $399, youâll get the unlimited site license, elite support, and advanced addons, including Stripe, WooCommerce, and more.</p>\n<h3>Our Verdict on Using Formidable Forms on Your Site</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/formidable-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Formidable Forms</a> is best-suited for users who want to build advanced forms with ease. </p>\n<p>This plugin comes with all the essential features you&#8217;d expect from an advanced WordPress form builder.</p>\n<p>We highly recommend Formidable Forms to any users who want to create user submitted forms, display form data on the frontend, perform powerful calculations, and more.</p>\n<p>We give it 4 out of 5 stars. Here&#8217;s the breakdown of our review scores:</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/formidable-forms/\">Formidable Forms Review: Build Advanced WordPress Forms</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/formidable-forms/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"43 Best Photography Themes for WordPress (2018)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-photography-themes-for-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-photography-themes-for-wordpress/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 18 Oct 2018 08:29:13 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:4:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Resources\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"best wordpress photography templates\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:33:\"create wordpress photography site\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"wordpress themes for photographers\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://www.isitwp.com/?p=223067\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:642:\"<p>Are you looking for the best photography themes for WordPress? If youâre a passionate photographer looking for the right platform to showcase your photos, creating a photography site in WordPress is the best option available. Using a WordPress photography theme, you can easily create a professional photography site and share your photos in a meaningful [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-photography-themes-for-wordpress/\">43 Best Photography Themes for WordPress (2018)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74360:\"<p>Are you looking for the best photography themes for WordPress? If youâre a passionate photographer looking for the right platform to showcase your photos, creating a photography site in WordPress is the best option available. Using a WordPress photography theme, you can easily create a professional photography site and share your photos in a meaningful way. </p>\n<p>In this article, weâll share the 43 best photography themes for WordPress.  </p>\n<h3>Creating a Photography Website with WordPress</h3>\n<p>WordPress is the best and most popular website platform available today. It&#8217;s <a href=\"https://w3techs.com/technologies/overview/content_management/all\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">used by over 31 percent of all websites online</a>. Thereâre numerous personal blogs as well as <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/popular-big-name-brands-using-wordpress/\">big name brands using WordPress</a> to create their websites. </p>\n<p>Thereâre 2 types of WordPress platforms: <strong>WordPress.org</strong> and <strong>WordPress.com</strong>. WordPress.com is a hosted platform with limited customization options, whereas the WordPress.org is the self-hosted platform that lets you customize limitlessly with thousands of themes and plugins. Thus, you&#8217;ll need to create your photography site on the self-hosted WordPress.org platform. </p>\n<p>For detailed information, you can check out our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-com-vs-wordpress-org-one-really-better/\">full comparison between WordPress.com and WordPress.org</a>.</p>\n<p>To create a photography site in WordPress.org, youâll need a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/difference-between-domain-name-and-web-hosting-revealed/\">domain name and a web hosting account</a>. Domain name refers to your websiteâs address on the internet, like Google.com or IsItWP.com. And, your web hosting account is where your siteâs content and files are stored online. </p>\n<p>A domain name usually costs around $14.99 per year and a web hosting plan costs around 7.99 per month. The combined cost of domain name and hosting can be quite expensive when youâre just starting out. </p>\n<p>Thankfully, weâve made a deal with <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> to offer our users a special discount. Bluehost is one of the largest and most popular hosting companies in the world. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg\" alt=\"create a blog on bluehost\" width=\"775\" height=\"483\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-218254\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-300x187.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/create-a-wordpress-account-on-bluehost-768x479.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/bluehost/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluehost</a> has agreed to provide you a web hosting plan for just $2.99 per month which is 60% off on the regular hosting price. In addition, youâll get a free domain name and SSL certificate with your purchase of web hosting. So, you can start your website for just $2.75 per month. </p>\n<p>If youâre new to WordPress, you can follow our step-by-step <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\">guide on how to create a WordPress site</a>.</p>\n<p>Now, letâs go ahead and take a look at the 43 best photography themes for WordPress. </p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/photography/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Photography</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/photography/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photography-wordpress-theme.jpg\" alt=\"photography-wordpress-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223094\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photography-wordpress-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photography-wordpress-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photography-wordpress-theme-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Photography is the most popular WordPress photography theme. Itâs the best-selling photography theme in the ThemeForest marketplace. The theme has received 4.5 stars out of 5 average rating from its users. </p>\n<p>The Photography theme comes with a complete set of features to allow you to create a top-notch photography site where you can present your photographs professionally and make money selling them. </p>\n<p>It features 70+ pre-designed photo gallery and portfolio templates, 9 thumbnail hover effects, 2 lightbox plugins, etc. Plus, it has various options to password protect galleries, photo proofing, client archive page, and customer protection. </p>\n<p>Thereâre 24 predefined demos covering white and dark skins. Each of the demos is ready for 1-click import so you can instantly start your photography site. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/photography/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Photography today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oshine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Oshine</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oshine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/oshine-theme-photography-site.jpg\" alt=\"oshine-theme-photography-site\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223103\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/oshine-theme-photography-site.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/oshine-theme-photography-site-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/oshine-theme-photography-site-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Oshine is a creative multipurpose theme suitable for building websites for photographers, artistic freelancers, and creative agencies. It comes with a highly intuitive visual page builder that allows you to create webpages easily, like a pro. </p>\n<p>The theme features 43 beautiful demos and over 100 pre-built sample pages which you can install and use in 1 click. Designed with professional photographers in mind, it has a modern and classy design, stunning sliders, carousels, password protected galleries, and much more. </p>\n<p>To make your site unique, it allows unlimited layout possibilities, complete control over colors and typography, multiple header styles, and infinite menu styles. Itâs a great theme and has 5 out of 5 stars average user ratings in Themeforest&#8217;s marketplace. </p>\n<p>Read our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/oshine/\">complete Oshine review</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/oshine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Oshine today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/novo-photography/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Novo Photography</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/novo-photography/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/novo-photography-theme.jpg\" alt=\"novo-photography-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223102\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/novo-photography-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/novo-photography-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/novo-photography-theme-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Novo Photography is an awesome WordPress theme for photographers, bloggers, agencies, and photo studios. It helps you build professional photography sites in no time flat. Itâs simple and easy to use &#8212; you can configure the theme settings and tweak the design per your desire without touching any code or hiring a developer. </p>\n<p>The theme features powerful photo protection options including password protection, right-click protection, and watermarks. These features help you secure photographs for professional use and protect your work from copying and theft. </p>\n<p>In addition, you can sell your photos easily from your website as it has fully featured eCommerce options. To quick-start your new photography website, you can import one of the predefined demos and customize it to suit your needs. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/novo-photography/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Novo Photography today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4. Divi</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/divi-theme-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"divi-theme-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223104\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/divi-theme-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/divi-theme-wordpress-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/divi-theme-wordpress-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Divi is one of the most powerful WordPress themes ever made. It utilizes the visual Divi Builder plugin, which allows you to create anything you can imagine with a simple drag and drop interface. Thereâre 46 beautiful content elements including gallery, portfolio, slider etc. in the plugin for building a photography site. </p>\n<p>Divi theme comes with 20+ stunning pre-made layouts and options to use several layouts from the Divi community. Additionally, it has tons of header and footer options that allow you to create a unique design for your site. </p>\n<p>In a nutshell, Divi offers limitless customization possibilities with an interface that&#8217;s so easy, even an absolute beginner can create something stunning. You can create any type of site, including a photography site, using this theme. </p>\n<p>Read our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/divi-theme-review/\">complete Divi review</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/divi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Divi today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/photocrati/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">5. Photocrati</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/photocrati/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photocrati-theme-wordpress.jpg\" alt=\"photocrati-theme-wordpress\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223107\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photocrati-theme-wordpress.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photocrati-theme-wordpress-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photocrati-theme-wordpress-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Photocrati is a fully responsive powerful photography theme for WordPress. The theme comes with a wide array of amazing features and functionalities to let you showcase your photos online. </p>\n<p>Thereâre 60+ starting designs, built-in galleries, eCommerce functionality, SEO tools, social media integration, and limitless customization options packed into this theme. You can create beautiful photo galleries and manage them professionally with eCommerce options, thumbnail customization, lightbox effects, slideshows, etc. </p>\n<p>The theme has multiple widget areas to help you customize your site design. Plus, you can fully control fonts, sizes, color, spacing, etc. on your theme to design your site beautifully. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/photocrati/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Photocrati today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">6. Themify Ultra</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ultra-theme-photography.jpg\" alt=\"ultra-theme-photography\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223105\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ultra-theme-photography.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ultra-theme-photography-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/ultra-theme-photography-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Themify Ultra is another powerful and super-flexible WordPress theme. You can create a wide variety of websites including agency, photography, wedding, restaurant, eCommerce, or fitness sites. </p>\n<p>The theme the Themify Builder page builder plugin built-in to allow you to design your site easily and beautifully. Itâs one of the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-page-builders-compared/\">most popular drag and drop page builders</a> available on the market. </p>\n<p>Themify Ultra theme offers over 10 pre-designed theme demos and over 60 design layouts which you can import with 1 click and use for quick customization. The photography demo of the theme features stunning sliders, masonry-style projects, and galleries. Itâs a great choice for stylish photography sites. </p>\n<p>Read our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/themify-ultra/\">complete Themify Ultra review</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themify-ultra/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Themify Ultra today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/uncode/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">7. Uncode</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/uncode/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/uncode-theme-photography-site.jpg\" alt=\"uncode-theme-photography-site\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223108\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/uncode-theme-photography-site.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/uncode-theme-photography-site-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/uncode-theme-photography-site-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Uncode is one of the most loved premium themes in the ThemeForest marketplace. The theme has made over 41,000 sales and received an average of 5 out of 5 stars from its users. You can use this theme for creating any type of site including a photography or photo blogging site. </p>\n<p>The theme comes bundled up with the famous drag and drop WPBakery Page Builder for WordPress which allows you to create any type of design you like with its intuitive drag and drop options. Plus, it has other premium plugins, namely Revolution Slider, LayerSlider, and iLightbox plugin, for creating sliders and lightbox galleries. </p>\n<p>It has 40+ pre-made demo sites, each built with a unique concept in mind. You can import a demo and start building your photography site instantly. </p>\n<p>Read our <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-themes/uncode/\">complete Uncode review</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/uncode/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Get started with Uncode today!</a></p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/photography-wiso/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">8. Photography Wiso</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/photography-wiso/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photography-wiso-theme.jpg\" alt=\"photography-wiso-theme\" width=\"775\" height=\"452\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-223109\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photography-wiso-theme.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photography-wiso-theme-300x175.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/photography-wiso-theme-768x448.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Photography Wiso is a creative WordPress theme for photographers. It comes with 34 ready-to-use demos and 95 albums and galleries that you can import in WordPress with 1 click. Then, you can customize, replace the dummy content with your original content, and publish your site online. </p>\n<p>Photography Wiso has advanced photography site features like gallery proofing, enab